comments.comment:

https://github.com/tensorflow/docs/blob/master/site/en/r1/guide/keras.ipynb https://colab.sandbox.google.com/github/tensorflow/docs/blob/master/site/en/r1/guide/keras.ipynb
But, really, they should point to the branch to avoid this: <denchmark-link:https://github.com/tensorflow/docs/blob/r2.0rc/site/en/guide/keras.ipynb>https://github.com/tensorflow/docs/blob/r2.0rc/site/en/guide/keras.ipynb</denchmark-link>

Links in TF1 guides and tutorials have been updated to point to the r2.0rcbranch:
https://colab.research.google.com/github/tensorflow/docs/blob/r2.0rc/site/en/guide/keras.ipynb https://github.com/tensorflow/docs/blob/r2.0rc/site/en/guide/keras.ipynb
